            "body": "`nlua_with` calls `handle_get_window` directly, which doesn't resolve 0 to `curwin`; acts like `win` isn't set.\n\nMeans not switching tab pages is probably the expected behaviour. (well, they are switched, but `_with` returns to the old `curwin` afterwards)",
